text: Areni Hamparian (; born 4 January 2002) is an Armenian footballer who plays as a midfielder for the Armenia women's national team. ==International career== Hamparian capped for Armenia at senior level in two friendlies against Lithuania on 4 and 6 March 2020. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Armenian women's footballers Category:Armenia women's international footballers
